Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:23.87,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}時の中を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:27.87,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}祈りのように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:31.41,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}天と土を結ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:36.63,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,960)\blur3}君がうたう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:23:00.99,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}静かなうた
