Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:47.25,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}你降生於夜幕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:54.79,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}小小的手掌向著廣大世界
